Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:02.61,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.61,0:00:05.85,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}High school student Shin'ichi was\Nforced to take a drug that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:08.75,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:11.82,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Time for another two-part episode!\NKogoro's club reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:15.28,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Even when old friendships fall apart,\Nthere's always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why won't you take us to your reunion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:47.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean why? It's my reunion...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:49.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You took me to the one five years ago, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't let the office close;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:55.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,what if something big happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:59.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But with you on vacation, the office would be closed no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:02.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to go to the hot spring, too! Right, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:04.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:08.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was going to treat you to a fancy meal instead of taking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:11.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll pass on the meal and take the hot spring trip instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:12.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:16.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Domestic flights are even more expensive than international ones lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:20.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna pay for three stinking people! Put yourself in my shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the truth comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:25.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He just robbed the bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:26.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:32.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You're not getting away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:34.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Stay back or I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:55.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! You caught a bank robber, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like taking candy from a baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:01.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when the great detective Kogoro Mouri is on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:06.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy! How did you make that brick do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:07.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:11.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I thought he was going to shoot you so I kicked it without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:15.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and it just happened to hit the robber's gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:18.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you saved his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:23.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're obligated to take the person
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:27.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who saved your life to the hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:30.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll come as Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s guardian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:34.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:39.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:45.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My company's right nearby. I came to have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Horikoshi-{\i1}san{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that you, Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:50.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming to the reunion at the hot spring again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who said—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yumi! Ran's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:07.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:10.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, Kogoro Mouri-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:14.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:17.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:22.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're not going to take the gun the robber had?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:32.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. I'm almost certain that his gun landed over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me someone on this street ran off with it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,during all the commotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:40.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to tell HQ and get it back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:44.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:46.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We only looked away for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who could've taken it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Eating while on a trip is the best thing ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:07.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to take that little brat to the reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:12.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem? You took me to the one five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:17.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were little at the time, so I couldn't leave you at home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:20.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't be able to attend this reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:24.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} hadn't saved your life, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:30.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could've caught that guy easy enough without the kid's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:34.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, did they ever find that missing gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:37.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what's the deal? The police haven't announced anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:42.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the police are investigating really hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it hasn't been used in any other crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:47.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and they don't seem to have any leads, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:51.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The gun was a Smith and Wesson M439.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:54.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That robber doesn't know much about guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:56.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He paid a lot of money for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:06:00.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he didn't know the difference between a real gun and a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's just a model gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:06.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No, the gun didn't break when I hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So if he actually did pay money for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}it was probably the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:20.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}{\a6}"Hot Spring Resort — Benkei"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is good to see you all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:42.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:46.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time since our last reunion five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:51.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...that everyone from the Beika University Judo Club has been together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:55.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This sure brings back memories of all those days of intense practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:59.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you to talk? You rarely ever came to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:02.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You constantly ditched practice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:06.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because you thought geniuses didn't need to train! Right, Mouri-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:11.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you were the only one who never won a single match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:12.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was because—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}knew{\i0} it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:18.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were lying whenever you boasted that you were invincible
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,during your college days, weren't you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}! It's good to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:28.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into her earlier today... She really has grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:29.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:32.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where've you been this entire time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The open-air bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The open-air bath?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a mixed-gender bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:40.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright, there was nobody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:43.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:47.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you two took a bath together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:53.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to get Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} to go, he was so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:57.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that sure was fun, scrubbing each other's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A nosebleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bath must've rushed the blood to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:04.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure he's not overexcited from seeing you naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:09.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he's not! He's still a kid, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:13.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I am so dead if she finds out who I really am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:16.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, so this is the boy Mouri-{\i1}kun{\i0} is taking care of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:18.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cute kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:20.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:25.63,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,High School Gym Teacher\NYukio Ayashiro (38)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:24.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Beika University's judo ace, Ayashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:25.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meetcha, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:32.09,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Model Shop Owner\NJun Omura (37)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:29.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Omura Jun, our judo club's biggest risk-taker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:32.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was our so-called "point-getter"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:36.55,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Cosmetic Company Employee\NYumi Horikoshi (37)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:36.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yumi Horikoshi, the beautiful manager of the judo club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:45.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Housewife\NNoriko Ayashiro (37)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name used to be Noriko Kimoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:42.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I also was the manager and idol of the judo club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:45.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm this man's wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:51.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiba Prefectural Police Detective\NKazushi Nakamichi (38)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:49.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kazushi Nakamichi. I was captain and central pillar of the team!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a police detective in Chiba prefecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:56.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, unlike this guy, I haven't quit my job halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:57.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Every one of them is a judo ace or idol...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:10.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And, as you all know, I'm Beika's greatest judo master and detective—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:11.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that our old college album?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I brought it so we could all look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:21.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Can't you hear people out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:30.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is from when we won 2nd place at the city tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:41.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamichi and Yumi were an item back then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:45.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. We cried together back then, didn't we, Omura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:51.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were definitely the judo club's Madonna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:54.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough. You're my husband now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:55.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:58.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are the two of you still—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:02.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly! I dumped this clod a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:05.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, he's already chosen someone to marry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:06.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting married, Nakamichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:16.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I had hoped to formally announce it to you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but the ceremony's going to be sometime this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:20.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My boss's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We met six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:27.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce her to you guys sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:31.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conversely, the former Madonna is still a single woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:36.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I might lose my job because of the bad economy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:39.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wish I were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:45.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding! I just wanted to see how you would react!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:49.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare us like that, Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:55.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means me and Omura-{\i1}kun{\i0} are the only unmarried ones left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:57.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:10:59.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:03.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stupid! It was a joke! Don't take it seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:12.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Isn't this picture from when we came here five years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I'm in the picture too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:15.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We took this picture in the ping-pong room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:20.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I stuck this photo in here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:23.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! What do you say we play some ping-pong now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:30.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're supposed to watch the fireworks in the evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:33.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. The fireworks start at 6:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have over three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:38.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we end before 6:00, we'll make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:39.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:43.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired for some reason. I'll be resting in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still the same as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She does everything at her own pace...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:51.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She just doesn't want people pulling her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's play some ping-pong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:56.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs and ping-pong go perfect together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been this raring to go for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:01.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a gym instructor, I can't afford to lose to the lot of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\a6}"Ping-Pong Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Get ready for another!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:11.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:12.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:13.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:16.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up next, so hurry on back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:23.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you win an individual award at a national championship before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:26.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, only once, when I was a junior in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:31.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you must've been the best member of the club, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:34.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there was a guy who was much better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:38.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never beat him even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You had someone that good in your club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:43.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him too, Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}. He's even staying at this inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:52.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Curveballs aren't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:57.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? That was pretty fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:59.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:08.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Yukio-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:09.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heads up, Noriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:16.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, how long are you two going to play so stupidly like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't it time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:21.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! It's already past 6:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:26.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! We have to hurry! The place'll be crowded!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:33.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return the rackets and stuff; you go find us a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We forgot to wake up Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about her. It's about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure someone's woken her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if we all forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:49.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:54.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh. They really should've left her alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! It started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to wake her up right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:21.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 201. This is her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:26.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks have started already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in, Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:33.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamichi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you go on ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:40.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to wake up Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:42.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:45.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She gets real grouchy whenever somebody wakes her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Nakamichi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked up a sweat playing ping-pong, so I took a quick bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I heard you two running...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:59.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange, since we're the only ones staying at this inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you still doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:04.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could ask you the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:08.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were washing off your sweat too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:12.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. But I was in the public bath unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:16.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}! It was definitely best that you didn't wake Yumi up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really grouchy when she wakes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:19.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:23.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll still be mad we didn't wake her up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:33.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is crowded! Don't let go of my hand, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:37.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:39.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:42.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Everyone was just with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:45.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They got separated from us in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll look around for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Omura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems like a restless kind of guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:56.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:16:00.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Omura went through the trouble to find a spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:01.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but not a single one of you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:06.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Omura went to look for you but never came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:07.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as is often the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:11.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I forgot where our spot was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:13.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some sake and forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:16.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys do things your own way far too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:18.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s still not up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Yeah, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:23.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be awake by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:29.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be pouting because she missed the fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:31.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You're all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:37.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we all go and wake up the judo club's Madonna?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:43.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to fear if we wake up the carefree woman together, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful now, don't say that in front of Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yumi! It's dinnertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:53.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:56.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you still asleep? I'm turning the light on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:11.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:12.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:17.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody but me and Mouri are to come in here, since we're detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:20.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Call the police immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:21.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:31.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bullet hole in her temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:34.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A gun in her right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:39.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Isn't that the gun the bank robber had!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:45.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The gun is a Smith and Wesson M439!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the barrel looks like it's been struck by something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:51.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, Yumi was at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:54.59,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:55.93,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.60,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:18:01.36,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My company's right nearby. I came to have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:07.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So Yumi picked up the gun because she had intended to use it from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:12.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means she had planned to commit suicide at our reunion...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:14.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:17.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's too early to make any conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:19.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait until the police get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:21.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good call...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:26.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Yumi? Why did you have to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:43.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Two hours until the police get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:48.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They said the streets are crowded because of the festival today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! We can't wait two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:53.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice! We'll have to do the autopsy ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:54.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:57.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have a camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:58.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us borrow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get it from my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:06.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought we would be giving Yumi an autopsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All finished here, Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her toes are beginning to stiffen too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:27.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a bit of time has passed since she died...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:29.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we check for death spots as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:34.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But given the amount of blood that she's lost, she might not have any...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:37.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's not wearing anything underneath!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:40.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:43.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:46.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, she's wearing a large yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:49.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was wearing a small one when she was in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:52.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the index finger of the hand that's holding the gun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:54.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't on the trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:57.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the strangest thing is that this bullet wound—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:01.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little—!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:05.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always getting in the way of my investigations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:05.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lousy kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:09.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find anything out, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:11.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the state of her rigor mortis,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:14.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi died over seven hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:18.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven hours ago... Which means around 3:00 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:21.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when we were in the ping-pong room, after she left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:25.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Most likely she returned to her room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:28.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and shot herself in the head with a gun she had hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:31.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's no question it was a suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:34.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would she kill herself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, she did say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:40.19,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I really wish I were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:42.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She really must've been thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.43,0:22:23.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, how did Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0} shoot herself in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:24.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:26.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask strange questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:27.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:28.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:32.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She put the gun up to her head like so and—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:36.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Mouri! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:39.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:40.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Nakamichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:42.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally when someone commits suicide with a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:45.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they stick the barrel against their head, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:46.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:49.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then her bullet wound is missing something vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:55.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! Burn marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:22:57.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:23:02.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you shoot a gun, a stream of hot air accompanies the bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:04.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you shoot with the gun against your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:07.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have to leave burn marks behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:09.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that there are none here means...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:13.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...that someone else shot her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.01,0:23:17.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone shot her and then tried to make it look like a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:20.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone in this inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:49.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! What are you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.83,0:23:52.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:54.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw who? The killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:58.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the supposedly-dead Yumi in a window upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:03.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch whoever killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.95,0:24:07.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I've finally figured out the trick the killer used!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:09.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You were the one who killed Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.45,0:24:17.45,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.45,0:24:22.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Benkei
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.76,0:24:24.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time... What does "Benkei" remind you of?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.68,0:24:26.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}An imposing stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.46,0:24:27.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Bingo!
